Hello happy easter,

I am Lawyer Hodela Egator by name, With due respect , I am contacting you
to help and assist me to get the deposit of (USD$13,580,000.00) my late
client Engineer left in his Bank before his sudden death with his wife and
their only Daughter on 25, July 2013.

To avoid confiscation by the bank, Please reply very urgent so that I will
tell you everything about this or kindly provide me with your own private
email address so that I can contact you myself with all the details at your
own will.

I hope to hear from you as soon as you read my message.

With kind regards and best wishes to you and your family.

Barrister Hodela Egator
